window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Peter Brettâ€™s <i>The Desert Spear</i> continues the post-apocalyptic adventure he began in his highly acclaimed debut, <i>The Warded Man</i>. </p> <p>The world remains under siege by demonkind stalking the land when the sun goes down. But a new hero has risen from the desert. Claiming to be the mythical Deliverer, Ahmann Jardir now rides alongside the allied desert tribes of Krasia. Jardir and his fellows are on an epic quest to vanquish the demons plaguing the world and bring humanity back from the brink of extinction.</p>"; 
